## ğŸ§  How It Works

| Component       | Role                                            |
|----------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| Firebase        | Stores all chat messages (text)                |
| Supabase        | Stores media files (images, video, audio)      |
| Realtime Combo | Keeps frontend light and costs within free-tier |
| No Auth         | Username only â€” no signup, login, or tracking  |

